reviewText: Will not play... its foreign and will  not play on American players.... go to a store to buy your dvds.
All three DVDs didn't work! Buyer be aware! If I could give no stars I would. I will be getting a refund!
It didn't play. it said to check region.
The dvd's are foreign, and don't work with US dvd's players...I was robbed of my money for useless dvd's.
